<h1><i>Candida tropicalis</i> MLST Databases</h1>
<p>The <i>Candida tropicalis</i> MLST website contains two linked databases - one for allelic profiles and sequences, the other for isolate information. This structure offers advantages over a single database system. Further details can be found <a href="http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2105/5/86/abstract">here</a>.</p>
<div class="refermessage">This database is hosted on PubMLST.org and is not affiliated with www.mlst.net.  Please cite accordingly.</div>
<table class="noborderlefttable"><tr><td>
