<div class="box">
<p>This MLST scheme was developed by Arianna Tavanti and <a href="mailto:f.odds@abdn.ac.uk">Frank Odds</a>.</p>
<p>Website and database managed by
<a href="mailto:keith.jolley@zoo.ox.ac.uk">Keith Jolley</a>, curated by <a href="mailto:f.odds@abdn.ac.uk">Frank Odds</a>.</p> 
<p>The use of this database is subject to the terms of the <a href="policy.shtml">policy document</a> and it should
be acknowledged in all publications that make use of it.  The preferred format for the acknowledgement can be found in the right-hand sidebar.</p>
<p>The <a href="http://pubmlst.org/ctropicalis/">primary <i>Candida tropicalis</i> MLST website</a> is hosted at the <a href="http://www.zoo.ox.ac.uk">Department of Zoology</a>, University of Oxford, UK.</p>
