<div id="rightpane">

<h2>Citing the database</h2>
<p>The preferred format for citing this website in publications is:</p>
<p>This publication made use of the Candida tropicalis Multi Locus Sequence Typing website (<a href="http://pubmlst.org/ctropicalis/">http://pubmlst.org/ ctropicalis/</a>) developed by Keith Jolley and sited at the University of Oxford (<a href="http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2105/5/86/abstract">Jolley et al. 2004, <i>BMC Bioinformatics</i>, <b>5</b>:86</a>). The development of this site has been funded by the Wellcome Trust.</p>

